1.0.0.name: wordpress/wp-strapthirteen
1.0.0.description: WP StrapThirteen is A TwentyThirteen child theme. The aim of this theme is to bring a bit of Bootstrap magic in to the default theme while still retaining the original look and feel of the parent theme.
